{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":527,"text":"Anyone in the room thought about sex today?"},{"time":3372,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":4532,"text":"Yeah, you did."},{"time":5737,"text":"Thank you for putting your hand up over there."},{"time":8203,"text":"Well, I'm here to provide you with"},{"time":9923,"text":"some biological validation"},{"time":11618,"text":"for your sordid daydreams."},{"time":13048,"text":"I'm here to tell you a few things"},{"time":14442,"text":"that you might not have known about wild sex."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17948,"text":"Now, when humans think about sex,"},{"time":19796,"text":"male and female forms"},{"time":21526,"text":"are generally what come to mind,"},{"time":23197,"text":"but for many millions of years,"},{"time":25650,"text":"such specific categories didn't even exist."},{"time":28271,"text":"Sex was a mere fusion of bodies"},{"time":30874,"text":"or a trickle of DNA"},{"time":32484,"text":"shared between two or more beings."},{"time":35026,"text":"It wasn't until about 500 million years ago"},{"time":37351,"text":"that we start to see structures akin to a penis"},{"time":40715,"text":"or a thing that gives DNA out,"},{"time":43373,"text":"and a vagina, something that receives it."},{"time":46527,"text":"Now invariably, you're probably thinking about"},{"time":48852,"text":"what belongs to our own species,"},{"time":51272,"text":"these very familiar structures,"},{"time":53170,"text":"but the diversity that we see in sexual structures"},{"time":55456,"text":"in the animal kingdom that has evolved"},{"time":57444,"text":"in response to the multitude of factors"},{"time":60092,"text":"surrounding reproduction"},{"time":61753,"text":"is pretty mind-blowing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64147,"text":"Penile diversity is especially profuse."},{"time":67788,"text":"So this is a paper nautilus."},{"time":69933,"text":"It's a close relative of squid and octopus,"},{"time":72843,"text":"and males have a hectocotylus."},{"time":75965,"text":"Just what is a hectocotylus?"},{"time":77715,"text":"A detachable, swimming penis."},{"time":81894,"text":"It leaves the [body of the male],"},{"time":84303,"text":"finds the female through\npheromonal cues in the water,"},{"time":87503,"text":"attaches itself to her body"},{"time":89414,"text":"and deposits the sperm."},{"time":90722,"text":"For many decades, biologists actually felt"},{"time":93246,"text":"that the hectocotylus was a\nseparate organism altogether."},{"time":97691,"text":"Now, the tapir is a mammal from South America."},{"time":100679,"text":"And the tapir has a prehensile penis."},{"time":103627,"text":"It actually has a level of dexterity in its penis"},{"time":106669,"text":"much akin to what we have with our hands."},{"time":109095,"text":"And it uses this dexterity"},{"time":110767,"text":"to bypass the vagina altogether"},{"time":112983,"text":"and deposit sperm directly into the female's uterus,"},{"time":116354,"text":"not to mention it's a pretty good size."},{"time":119908,"text":"The biggest penis in the animal kingdom,"},{"time":121837,"text":"however, is not that of the tapir."},{"time":123532,"text":"The biggest penis-to-body-size ratio"},{"time":125864,"text":"in the animal kingdom actually belongs"},{"time":127558,"text":"to the meager beach barnacle,"},{"time":129809,"text":"and this video is actually showing you"},{"time":132001,"text":"what the human penis would look like"},{"time":134085,"text":"if it were the same size as that of a barnacle."},{"time":137546,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":140732,"text":"Mm-hm. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":142995,"text":"So with all of this diversity in structure,"},{"time":145793,"text":"one might think, then, that penises"},{"time":147950,"text":"are fitting neatly into vaginas all over the place"},{"time":150921,"text":"for the purposes of successful reproduction."},{"time":152998,"text":"Simply insert part A into slot B,"},{"time":155543,"text":"and we should all be good to go."},{"time":157618,"text":"But of course, that doesn't exactly happen,"},{"time":159947,"text":"and that's because we can't\njust take form into account."},{"time":162875,"text":"We have to think about function as well,"},{"time":165157,"text":"and when it comes to sex,"},{"time":166947,"text":"function relates to the contributions made"},{"time":169473,"text":"by the gametes, or the sperm and the eggs."},{"time":172272,"text":"And these contributions are far from equal."},{"time":175606,"text":"Eggs are very expensive to make,"},{"time":177992,"text":"so it makes sense for females to be very choosy"},{"time":180943,"text":"about who she shares them with."},{"time":183380,"text":"Sperm, on the other hand, is abundant and cheap,"},{"time":187193,"text":"so it makes more sense for males"},{"time":189045,"text":"to have a more-sex-is-better strategy"},{"time":191195,"text":"when it comes to siring members"},{"time":192607,"text":"of future generations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194453,"text":"So how do animals cope"},{"time":196165,"text":"with these very incongruent\nneeds between the sexes?"},{"time":199050,"text":"I mean, if a female doesn't choose a particular male,"},{"time":202299,"text":"or if she has the ability to store sperm"},{"time":204738,"text":"and she simply has enough,"},{"time":206415,"text":"then it makes more sense for her to spend her time"},{"time":208488,"text":"doing other biologically relevant things:"},{"time":211166,"text":"avoiding predators, taking care of offspring,"},{"time":214023,"text":"gathering and ingesting food."},{"time":216193,"text":"This is, of course, bad news for any male"},{"time":218506,"text":"who has yet to make a deposit in her sperm bank,"},{"time":221057,"text":"and this sets the scene for\nsome pretty drastic strategies"},{"time":224162,"text":"for successful fertilization."},{"time":227468,"text":"This is bedbug sex,"},{"time":229475,"text":"and it's aptly termed traumatic insemination."},{"time":233749,"text":"Males have a spiked, barbed penis"},{"time":236543,"text":"that they literally stab into the female,"},{"time":239147,"text":"and they don't stab it anywhere near her vagina."},{"time":242008,"text":"They stab it anywhere in her body,"},{"time":244143,"text":"and the sperm simply migrates"},{"time":245940,"text":"through her hemolymph to her ovaries."},{"time":249244,"text":"If a female gets too many stab wounds,"},{"time":251388,"text":"or if a stab wound happens to become infected,"},{"time":253734,"text":"she can actually die from it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256113,"text":"Now if you've ever been out for a nice,"},{"time":257884,"text":"peaceful walk by the lake"},{"time":259775,"text":"and happened to see some ducks having sex,"},{"time":262517,"text":"you've undoubtedly been alarmed,"},{"time":264212,"text":"because it looks like gang rape."},{"time":266723,"text":"And quite frankly, that's exactly what it is."},{"time":269384,"text":"A group of males will grab a female,"},{"time":271604,"text":"hold her down,"},{"time":272773,"text":"and ballistically ejaculate their spiral-shaped penis"},{"time":277203,"text":"into her corkscrew-shaped vagina"},{"time":280287,"text":"over and over and over again."},{"time":283193,"text":"From flaccid to ejaculation in less than a second."},{"time":286982,"text":"Now the female actually\ngets the last laugh, though,"},{"time":289117,"text":"because she can actually manipulate her posture"},{"time":291944,"text":"so as to allow the sperm of certain suitors"},{"time":295049,"text":"better access to her ovaries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298311,"text":"Now, I like to share stories\nlike this with my audiences"},{"time":300421,"text":"because, yeah, we humans,"},{"time":301877,"text":"we tend to think sex, sex is fun, sex is good,"},{"time":305022,"text":"there's romance, and there's orgasm."},{"time":307263,"text":"But orgasm didn't actually evolve"},{"time":308945,"text":"until about 65 million years ago"},{"time":311031,"text":"with the advent of mammals."},{"time":312798,"text":"But some animals had it going\non quite a bit before that."},{"time":315662,"text":"There are some more primitive ways"},{"time":317416,"text":"of pleasing one's partner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319817,"text":"Earwig males have either"},{"time":321873,"text":"really large penile appendages"},{"time":323631,"text":"or really small ones."},{"time":325032,"text":"It's a very simple genetically inherited trait"},{"time":327853,"text":"and the males are not otherwise any different."},{"time":329839,"text":"Those that have long penile appendages"},{"time":331801,"text":"are not bigger or stronger"},{"time":333569,"text":"or otherwise any different at all."},{"time":335073,"text":"So going back to our biological minds, then,"},{"time":337614,"text":"we might think that females should choose"},{"time":339731,"text":"to have sex with the guys that\nhave the shorter appendages,"},{"time":342712,"text":"because she can use her time for other things:"},{"time":345277,"text":"avoiding predators, taking care of young,"},{"time":346953,"text":"finding and ingesting food."},{"time":348801,"text":"But biologists have repeatedly observed"},{"time":351617,"text":"that females choose to have sex"},{"time":353585,"text":"with the males that have the long appendages."},{"time":357714,"text":"Why do they do this?"},{"time":359677,"text":"Well, according to the biological literature,"},{"time":362076,"text":"\"During copulation, the genitalia of certain males"},{"time":364903,"text":"may elicit more favorable female responses"},{"time":367523,"text":"through superior mechanical\nor stimulatory interaction"},{"time":370600,"text":"with the female reproductive tract.\""},{"time":374158,"text":"Mm-hm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376549,"text":"These are Mexican guppies,"},{"time":378486,"text":"and what you see on their upper maxilla"},{"time":380617,"text":"is an outgrowth of epidermal filaments,"},{"time":383019,"text":"and these filaments basically form"},{"time":384864,"text":"a fish mustache, if you will."},{"time":387462,"text":"Now males have been observed to prod"},{"time":389804,"text":"the female's genital opening"},{"time":391468,"text":"prior to copulating with her,"},{"time":393415,"text":"and in what I have lovingly termed\nthe Magnum, P.I. hypothesis,"},{"time":396924,"text":"females are overwhelmingly more likely to be found"},{"time":400936,"text":"with males that have these fish mustaches."},{"time":404901,"text":"A little guppy porn for you right there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408198,"text":"So we've seen very different strategies"},{"time":410954,"text":"that males are using when it comes to"},{"time":413192,"text":"winning a female partner."},{"time":414788,"text":"We've seen a coercion strategy in which\nsexual structures are used in a forceful way"},{"time":419776,"text":"to basically make a female have sex."},{"time":421549,"text":"We've also seen a titillation strategy"},{"time":423606,"text":"where males are actually"},{"time":425543,"text":"pleasing their female partners into choosing them"},{"time":427691,"text":"as a sex partner."},{"time":429410,"text":"Now unfortunately, in the animal kingdom,"},{"time":431855,"text":"it's the coercion strategy that we see"},{"time":434271,"text":"time and time again."},{"time":436010,"text":"It's very common in many phyla,"},{"time":438357,"text":"from invertebrates to avian species,"},{"time":440990,"text":"mammals, and, of course, even in primates."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443536,"text":"Now interestingly, there \nare a few mammalian species"},{"time":447073,"text":"in which females have evolved specialized genitalia"},{"time":450305,"text":"that doesn't allow for sexual coercion to take place."},{"time":454974,"text":"Female elephants and female hyenas"},{"time":457342,"text":"have a penile clitoris,"},{"time":459716,"text":"or an enlarged clitoral tissue that hangs externally,"},{"time":463523,"text":"much like a penis,"},{"time":465082,"text":"and in fact it's very difficult to sex these animals"},{"time":467466,"text":"by merely looking at their external morphology."},{"time":470633,"text":"So before a male can insert\nhis penis into a female's vagina,"},{"time":474225,"text":"she has to take this penile clitoris"},{"time":476080,"text":"and basically inside-out it in her own body."},{"time":479643,"text":"I mean, imagine putting a penis into another penis."},{"time":482580,"text":"It's simply not going to happen"},{"time":484112,"text":"unless the female is on board with the action."},{"time":487434,"text":"Now, even more interesting is the fact"},{"time":489247,"text":"that elephant and hyena societies"},{"time":491256,"text":"are entirely matriarchal:"},{"time":493685,"text":"they're run by females, groups of females,"},{"time":496187,"text":"sisters, aunts and offspring,"},{"time":498433,"text":"and when young males attain sexual maturity,"},{"time":501636,"text":"they're turfed out of the group."},{"time":503513,"text":"In hyena societies, adult males"},{"time":505596,"text":"are actually the lowest on the social scale."},{"time":508858,"text":"They can take part in a kill only after"},{"time":511291,"text":"everybody else, including the offspring."},{"time":514021,"text":"So it seems that when you take the penis power"},{"time":516339,"text":"away from a male,"},{"time":518177,"text":"you take away all the social power he has."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522236,"text":"So what are my take-home\nmessages from my talk today?"},{"time":524878,"text":"Well, sex is just so much more"},{"time":527559,"text":"than insert part A into slot B"},{"time":530158,"text":"and hope that the offspring run around everywhere."},{"time":533300,"text":"The sexual strategies and reproductive structures"},{"time":535957,"text":"that we see in the animal kingdom basically"},{"time":538980,"text":"dictate how males and females\nwill react to each other,"},{"time":542908,"text":"which then dictates how populations and societies"},{"time":545654,"text":"form and evolve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547284,"text":"So it may not be surprising to any of you"},{"time":549753,"text":"that animals, including ourselves,"},{"time":551561,"text":"spend a good amount of time thinking about sex,"},{"time":555171,"text":"but what might surprise you is the extent to which"},{"time":558347,"text":"so many other aspects of their lives and our lives"},{"time":562418,"text":"are influenced by it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":564240,"text":"So thank you, and happy daydreaming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566203,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}